com.im.njams.sdk.communication

Interface Sender

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, ClasspathValidator
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractSender, HttpSender, HttpsSender, JmsSender, NjamsSender

    public interface Sender
extends AutoCloseable, ClasspathValidator
    This interface must be implemented to create a nJAMS Sender Inplementations which can send Project and Logmessages to nJAMS Server.
    Author:
    bwand
